estimateSolarActivity

public int estimateSolarActivity(int angle)
Attemps to estimate radio wave absorbtion caused by ionization of layer D using the following rationale: IF in this direction +/-SOME degress has been more activity at time 24-26 h before the last two hours THEN solar activity is high i.e. activity is number of spots today MINUS yesterday.
